---
layout: ../layouts/base.njk

pagination:
  data: tournaments
  size: 1
  alias: tournament

permalink: "sport/{{ tournament.sport }}/{{ tournament.id }}/index.html"

eleventyComputed:
  title: "Where to Watch {{ tournament.name }} {{ tournament.season }}"
  description: "Watch {{ tournament.name }} live worldwide. Find streaming services, TV channels, pricing and country-specific broadcast information."
---

<header class="sport-hero">
  <div class="sport-hero-inner">

    <div class="hero-eyebrow">
      {{ tournament.sport | upper }}
    </div>

    <h1 class="sport-hero-title">
      {{ tournament.name }}
    </h1>

    <p class="sport-hero-sub">
      {{ tournament.description }}
    </p>

  </div>
</header>

<main class="sport-main">

<section class="stream-section">

<div class="section-label">
Overview
</div>

<p>
{{ tournament.name }} {{ tournament.season }} can be streamed across multiple countries.
Select your country below to see official streaming platforms and TV broadcasters.
</p>

</section>

<section class="stream-section">

<h2>
Available Countries
</h2>

<ul class="country-list">

{% for countryCode, info in tournament.broadcasts %}

{% set platformData = platformLookup[info.streaming] %}

<li>
  <a href="/sport/{{ tournament.sport }}/{{ tournament.id }}/{{ countryCode }}/">
    {{ countryCode | capitalize }}
  </a>
  {% if platformData %}
  <span class="stream-price {% if platformData.isFree %}free-tag{% else %}paid-tag{% endif %}">
    {% if platformData.isFree %}FREE{% else %}PAID{% endif %}
  </span>
  {% endif %}
</li>

{% endfor %}

</ul>

</section>

<section class="stream-section">

<h2>
About {{ tournament.name }}
</h2>

<p>
{{ tournament.description }}
</p>

<p>
Fans worldwide search for where to watch {{ tournament.name }} live.
This guide provides country-specific streaming information and official broadcast partners.
</p>

</section>

<section class="stream-section">

<h2>
Frequently Asked Questions
</h2>

<h3>
Where can I watch {{ tournament.name }}?
</h3>

<p>
Select your country above to view available streaming services and television broadcasters.
</p>

<h3>
Is {{ tournament.name }} available online?
</h3>

<p>
Yes. Streaming availability varies by country and broadcasting rights.
</p>

</section>

<section class="stream-section">

<div class="section-label">
Related {{ tournament.sport | capitalize }} Tournaments
</div>

<ul>

{% for item in tournaments %}

{% if item.sport == tournament.sport and item.id != tournament.id %}

<li>
<a href="/sport/{{ item.sport }}/{{ item.id }}/">
{{ item.name }}
</a>
</li>

{% endif %}

{% endfor %}

</ul>

</section>

</main>
